column1: #: description: Nuclear modification factor for inclusive J$/psi$ as a function of pT in Pb-Pb collisions at $\sqrt{{s}_{NN}}$ = 5.02 TeV for 40-90% centrality interval and 2.5<y< 4. The given systematic uncertainties are the uncorrelated systematic ones over pT. The correlated systematic uncertainties over pT amount to 3.99%. ;
